### ============================================================
### UPLOAD MODULE — HTTP Test
### Chức năng: Upload & xóa hình ảnh trên Cloudinary
### ============================================================

### 1. Đăng nhập
POST http://localhost:9999/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "minh.pham@gmail.com",
  "password": "Test@123",
  "deviceToken": "device_token_test_upload",
  "deviceType": "Postman",
  "deviceName": "Test Client"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### ============================================================
### 2. Upload icon (cho danh mục, ví, sự kiện, mục tiêu...)
### Thay đường dẫn file bằng ảnh thật trên máy bạn
### ============================================================
POST http://localhost:9999/api/upload/image?type=icon
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test_icon.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< D:/path/to/your/icon.png
--boundary--

### ============================================================
### 3. Upload avatar (cho tài khoản người dùng)
### ============================================================
POST http://localhost:9999/api/upload/image?type=avatar
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="avatar.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< D:/path/to/your/avatar.jpg
--boundary--

### ============================================================
### 4. Xóa ảnh theo URL
### Thay URL bằng URL thật từ kết quả upload
### ============================================================
DELETE http://localhost:9999/api/upload/image?imageUrl=https://res.cloudinary.com/xxx/image/upload/v123/smartmoney/icons/abc.png
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

